{"tid":1183653,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「人生的每一天都浪費不起：別想太多，做了再說」","createTime":"2019-06-03T05:47:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T15:48:51.000Z","uid":76885,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cb1aa8eb5ee1421ed97dbda0ec22476250be5c54","tid":1183653,"uid":76885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T05:47:18.000Z","msg":"1<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cheers.com.tw/article/article.action?id=5093645\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cheers.com.tw%2Farticle%2Farticle.action%3Fid%3D5093645&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewOJhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=e47e7544\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cheers.com.tw/article/article.action?id=5093645</a><br />\n<br />\n<em>因為思考總是輕鬆容易，但付諸行動需要勇氣及力氣。</em><br />\n<em>與其自己想太多，為何不先做了再說？</em><br />\n<em>別把時間浪費在自己的猶豫不決、別把時間浪費在沒人觀看的內心小劇場，人生不過就是3萬天，而我們每一天都浪費不起。</em><br />\n<em>別想太多，做了再說。</em><br />\n<br />\n2<br />\n假如你可以真係唔再考慮成功既可能性，而做左先算。<br />\n<br />\n你會做d咩？"},{"pid":"54ba4018293405cf3ee319599a33a3fb52cfe17d","tid":1183653,"uid":80015,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T06:25:56.000Z","msg":"強姦"},{"pid":"b3ccc93d4f69b99ac7ca24d01fccfde327f0cbe2","tid":1183653,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54ba4018293405cf3ee319599a33a3fb52cfe17d","tid":1183653,"uid":80015,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T06:25:56.000Z","msg":"強姦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T06:33:39.000Z","msg":"不要暗戀"},{"pid":"c733211c6bf138cc89ad6841a12bed3cfc61f624","tid":1183653,"uid":31318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T15:26:30.000Z","msg":"知而行難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14afc31d446490af38bf050b41f0e6c471166db8","tid":1183653,"uid":76885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c733211c6bf138cc89ad6841a12bed3cfc61f624","tid":1183653,"uid":31318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T15:26:30.00